            <num>•</num>
            <content>
              <p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/skills-england-report-driving-growth-and-widening-opportunities"><u>Skills England report: driving growth and widening opportunities - GOV.UK (www.gov.uk)</u></a> (24 September 2024)</p>
            </content>
          </subparagraph>
