              <p><a href="https://questions-statements.parliament.uk/written-statements/detail/2024-07-22/hcws14"><u>Written statements - Written questions, answers and statements - UK Parliament</u></a> (22 July 2024) </p>
            </content>
          </subparagraph>
        </paragraph>
      </section>
